Generic single-database configuration with async support.

This directory contains Alembic migration scripts for the MealFrame database.

## Common Commands

Generate a new migration:
    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description of changes"

Apply all migrations:
    alembic upgrade head

Rollback one migration:
    alembic downgrade -1

View migration history:
    alembic history

View current version:
    alembic current

## Notes

- Always review autogenerated migrations before applying
- Test migrations both upgrade and downgrade
- Migration files are in alembic/versions/
- Database URL is configured from environment variables via app.config
